Profile: CervicalDiagnosticReportLtCervical
Parent: DiagnosticReport
Id: cervical-diagnostic-report-lt-cervical
Title: "DiagnosticReport: Cervical Cancer Screening and Diagnostic Report"
Description: "Comprehensive diagnostic report for cervical cancer screening and diagnostics in the Lithuanian pathway."
* ^url = $cervical-diagnostic-report-lt-cervical-url
* ^publisher = "HL7 Lithuania"
* status 1..1
* category 1..1
* category = $observation-category#exam
* code 1..1
* code = $sct#71341001 "Screening for malignant neoplasm of cervix (procedure)"
* subject 1..1
* subject only Reference(PatientLt)
* effective[x] 1..1
* issued 1..1
* performer 0..*
* performer only Reference(PractitionerLt or PractitionerRoleLt or OrganizationLt)
* resultsInterpreter 0..*
* resultsInterpreter only Reference(PractitionerLt or PractitionerRoleLt)
* result 0..*
* result only Reference(
    HpvTestResultLtCervical or
    CytologyConclusionLtCervical or
    ColposcopyFindingLtCervical or
    Observation
  )
* supportingInfo 0..*
* supportingInfo.reference only Reference(
    DiagnosticReport or
    Procedure
  )
* specimen 0..*
* specimen only Reference($EuSpecimenUrl)
* conclusion 0..1
* conclusionCode 0..*